OL,3,CRussian captain appears in court over
OL,4,Cfatal North Sea crash
OL,6,FMotin, of Primorsky, St Petersburg,
OL,7,Fappeared by videolink from Hull prison
OL,8,Fat the Old Bailey on Monday accused of
OL,9,Fgross negligence manslaughter.
OL,11,FIn the absence of a Russian
OL,12,Finterpreter to assist the defendant,
OL,13,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC adjourned his
OL,14,Fplea hearing until 30 May.
OL,16,FMotin, who is facing a provisional
OL,17,Ftrial on 12 January 2026, was remanded
OL,18,Finto custody.
