OL,3,CRussian captain appears in court over
OL,4,Cfatal North Sea crash
OL,6,FThirty-six people from the Solong and
OL,7,Fthe Stena Immaculate were rescued
OL,8,Ffollowing the crash about 12 miles off
OL,9,FWithernsea, but Mr Pernia could not be
OL,10,Flocated.
OL,12,FHe was working in the forward deck of
OL,13,Fthe Solong, in the area where there
OL,14,Fwas an explosion.
OL,16,FThe collision happened at about 9.47am
OL,17,Fat 10.2 nautical miles from the
OL,18,Fnearest point on the coast, a previous
OL,19,Fhearing was told.
